T02D2308:248b-0: @248b * // mu stegs la gdams pa bzhugs//
T02D2308:248b-2: # // aa ai rnal 'byor chen po kye //
T02D2308:248b-3: gnyis su med pa'i bde ba ni //
T02D2308:248b-4: rang byung rtsol ba bral ba ste //
T02D2308:248b-5: bsam gyis mi khyab ngo mtshar che //
T02D2308:248b-6: thabs chen rnam gnyis ma bstan par //
T02D2308:248b-7: de nyid rtogs pa med pa ste //
T02D2308:248b-8: sems nyid nor bu rin chen la //
T02D2308:248b-9: 'dod pa med pa'i tshul gyis rtogs //
T02D2308:248b-10: shes rab lhun gyis grub pa yi //
T02D2308:248b-11: ye shes chen po bsam mi khyab /
T02D2308:248b-12: gnyis med lam gyi 'jug pa dang //
T02D2308:248b-13: zung 'jug chen po rgyal ba'i thugs //
T02D2308:248b-14: sgrib med nyi ma gsal ba yis //
T02D2308:248b-15: dngos po ma lus snang bar byed //
T02D2308:248b-16: don dam ye shes chen po la //
T02D2308:248b-17: kun rdzob rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor shar //
T02D2308:248b-18: mnyam nyid sems la goms pa ni //
T02D2308:248b-19: skyes bu seng ge lta bur brjid //
T02D2308:248b-21: mi dbang ma yi lto na gnas //
T02D2308:248b-22: sel med shes pa ma bcos pa //
T02D2308:248b-23: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor chen po yin //
T02D2308:248b-24: gnyen pos bcos dang dgag pa med //
T02D2308:248b-25: rang lugs ye shes chen por gsal //
T02D2308:248b-26: mnyam pa'i gdeng dang ldan pa yis //
T02D2308:248b-27: dpa' bo mi mthun g-yul las rgyal //
T02D2308:248b-28: de ltar brtul zhugs spyod pa yis //
T02D2308:248b-29: rnal 'byor che la gnas par bya //
T02D2308:248b-30: rma bya dug gis mdzes pa ltar //
T02D2308:248b-31: dpa' bo nyon mongs rgyan du 'gyur //
T02D2308:248b-32: rgyal ba gshegs yul phrin las bzhi //
T02D2308:248b-33: de bzhin rnal 'byor pas shes mdzod //
T02D2308:248b-34: 'dzin med ye shes chen po'i mes //
T02D2308:248b-35: rtog pa'i bag chags sreg par byed //
T02D2308:248b-36: sgrib bral byang chub sems la ni //
T02D2308:248b-37: dri mas nam yang gos pa med //
T02D2308:248b-38: rin thang med pa'i nor bu de //
T02D2308:248b-39: bsod nams phun tshogs dag la mnga' //
T02D2308:248b-40: ldan min sems kyi gter mdzod de //
T02D2308:248b-41: bla ma'i drin thob rnams la gsal //
T02D2308:248b-42: rig byed sems kyi rnam pa ni //
T02D2308:248b-43: man ngag rim pas thag bcad de //
T02D2308:248b-44: rang bzhin de ltar yid chas pas //
T02D2308:248b-45: rnam par mi rtog don dam mo //
T02D2308:248b-46: chos rnams nam mkha' mtshon pa ste //
T02D2308:249a-0: ngo bo sems kyi yul las @249a * //
T02D2308:249a-2: smig rgyu'i rgyu yang nam mkha' la //
T02D2308:249a-3: sna tshogs snang ba de ltar byos //
T02D2308:249a-4: theg mchog yangs pa zab mo'i lam //
T02D2308:249a-5: dmigs med spros pa kun las 'das //
T02D2308:249a-6: chos kyi dbyings su mnyam pa yi //
T02D2308:249a-7: de nyid don chen blo la 'char //
T02D2308:249a-8: yod med sems kyi yul las 'das //
T02D2308:249a-9: re dogs 'dzin pa mtha' nas sangs //
T02D2308:249a-10: chos rnams du ma ro gcig phyir //
T02D2308:249a-11: sgom dang mi sgom rtsol ba bral //
T02D2308:249a-12: sems nyid ye nas sangs rgyas pas //
T02D2308:249a-13: chos nyid gzhan du bsgom mi dgos //
T02D2308:249a-14: yin par shes pa blo thag chod //
T02D2308:249a-15: spangs thob yon tan de tsam mo //
T02D2308:249a-16: rnam par rtog dang mi rtog kyang //
T02D2308:249a-17: rang bzhin shes pas yongs mi nyams //
T02D2308:249a-18: ngo bo nyid kyis ma skyes pas //
T02D2308:249a-19: rjes med bya lam bcos su med //
T02D2308:249a-20: mi mthun gnyen po dbyer med pa //
T02D2308:249a-21: de shes 'bad pa'i blo dang bral //
T02D2308:249a-22: mnyam gzhag chen po'i dgongs pa ste //
T02D2308:249a-23: gang la de yod rig ba can //
T02D2308:249a-24: gcer bu ral ba'i gtsug phud can //
T02D2308:249a-26: 'jig rten sa la mi dor zhing //
T02D2308:249a-27: de nyid ye shes mthong ba med //
T02D2308:249a-28: kun gzhi rnam dag dkar po la //
T02D2308:249a-29: snang ba sna tshogs ri mo bkra //
T02D2308:249a-30: ji srid nam mkha'i mtha' yi bar //
T02D2308:249a-31: shes rab sprul pa bsam mi khyab //
T02D2308:249a-32: sprul tsam nyid na ma nges te //
T02D2308:249a-33: mnyam nyid rgyal po'i ngang la gnas //
T02D2308:249a-34: dbang bsgyur ye shes chen po ste //
T02D2308:249a-35: de nyid gzhan min bdag po nyid //
T02D2308:249a-36: sgra tshad lung gi mtshon cha yang //
T02D2308:249a-37: skye med rang byung ngang nas shar //
T02D2308:249a-38: tshangs pa dbang phyug la sogs kyang //
T02D2308:249a-39: yi ge shes par ma mthong ngo //
T02D2308:249a-40: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes de //
T02D2308:249a-41: rtsol bas ring du spong gyur pas //
T02D2308:249a-42: rtsol med bla ma'i zhal las ni //
T02D2308:249a-43: legs nyes ring thang bral ba ltos //
T02D2308:249a-44: rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen po tilli pas //
T02D2308:249a-45: rgyal po sang grags seng ge'i sgo drung du mu
T02D2308:249a-46: stegs pa la gdams pa chos nyid bsam gyis mi
